{"id": 811, "genre": 1001, "title": "春晚你有啥想吐槽的？", "description": "哈哈哈哈哈哈什么鬼。", "record_count": 15089, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183642X1abGnLg0cQy9HUD.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-02-07T19:57:57Z", "options": [{"id": 66304, "content": "想吐。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 547319}, {"id": 47616, "content": "还不如看两集我在故宫修文物来的温暖", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456347}, {"id": 47617, "content": "没看 明天上午醒来看", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 250675}, {"id": 47873, "content": "只有谭维维唱出了晚会的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460890}, {"id": 47618, "content": "可以成立一个春晚吐槽微笑群", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 413231}, {"id": 47874, "content": "中国春梦。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142863}, {"id": 47619, "content": "全程小S冷漠脸。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 414097}, {"id": 48131, "content": "加油男孩长得好像Tfboys！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 267220}, {"id": 48899, "content": "我喝多了，一点没看。事后也没看重播，我想以后过年，不需要看春晚这个过时无趣的东东了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018157}, {"id": 47620, "content": "我觉得今年的春晚还是有创新的，虽然舞蹈还是老样子，但第二个小品不错，起码比第一个好。句号演的那个比较让感兴趣的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 364969}, {"id": 48132, "content": "做作，就像上小学时候的思想品德课一样，各种好品质，大道理，别扭！", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 369807}, {"id": 49924, "content": "没有六小龄童！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469271}, {"id": 47621, "content": "为什么一个人民联欢晚会要那么多政治洗脑，平时也就算了跨年联欢还不放过么", "image": null, "praise_count": 158, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 185304}, {"id": 47877, "content": "红色正剧", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461394}, {"id": 48901, "content": "别老给我们镜头了，真笑不出来。---现场观众", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 457935}, {"id": 47622, "content": "老公一出来，整个后宫都炸了", "image": "img/option/option/20160607194100TCzv3DFwjxbtXBKN.jpg", "praise_count": 253, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 177790}, {"id": 47878, "content": "数十年如一日", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461393}, {"id": 48390, "content": "应该向往年春晚总导演道歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234175}, {"id": 53254, "content": "怎么还会有春晚，不能停吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487761}, {"id": 47623, "content": "心疼老大爷当道具", "image": null, "praise_count": 27, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151325}, {"id": 47624, "content": "周涛最好看，主持最正常", "image": null, "praise_count": 34, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 438332}, {"id": 47880, "content": "看了节目单，果断没看", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 417375}, {"id": 47625, "content": "内心毫无波澜甚至有些饿", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004807iC5chfPWYHopsvUz.jpg", "praise_count": 31, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460474}, {"id": 47881, "content": "政治卷子又有材料题了", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265470}, {"id": 48393, "content": "春晚你好，春晚再见，春晚不见", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 212731}, {"id": 47626, "content": "看的要睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 393935}, {"id": 48906, "content": "身在曹营心在汉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465600}, {"id": 47883, "content": "没看哈，来这里收集点段子当谈资。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461425}, {"id": 48651, "content": "敬业福", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 464199}, {"id": 50187, "content": "央视报道满意度百分之一百", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467873}, {"id": 47628, "content": "感觉身在北朝鲜。", "image": null, "praise_count": 728, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 430445}, {"id": 47884, "content": "庄重的娱乐节目转变为尴尬的政治宣传", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461384}, {"id": 48908, "content": "我默默的拿出了我的红领巾", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 465593}, {"id": 53260, "content": "春晚像宗教，从精神寄托到现代社会的微弱存在感", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 487761}, {"id": 47629, "content": "中国梦什么的 好无聊*_*", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461074}, {"id": 47885, "content": "现场观众应该请我是歌手的观众啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 455305}, {"id": 47630, "content": "解放军叔叔被实力冷场", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004851Wmx4dwDczU9gafY0.jpg", "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256936}, {"id": 47886, "content": "必须戴着红领巾和团徽去看啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461438}, {"id": 48142, "content": "开场白不忘舔台湾(ฅ>ω<*ฅ)", "image": "img/option/option/20160606004711g81FqQp7XsRk0fYc.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462026}, {"id": 47631, "content": "咻～咻咻～～咔嚓，咔嚓～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217672}, {"id": 47887, "content": "敬业福", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 256931}, {"id": 47632, "content": "看到现在居然一个好看的节目都没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461081}, {"id": 47888, "content": "你我本无缘，全靠党的章程死撑", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 429443}, {"id": 48656, "content": "像是一锅大烩菜，乱七八糟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450169}, {"id": 49424, "content": "某主持话：如果大家都能遵道德，守道德……所以，法律呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467197}, {"id": 48657, "content": "办这台晚会你出钱了吗？看这台晚会你出钱了吗？想看就看！不想看就不看！晚会又不是为你们办的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 462601}, {"id": 49937, "content": "Y姓男星是我见过第一个假唱把自己唱哭的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 469405}, {"id": 47634, "content": "朱迅的鼻影打得，已经有点像黄渤了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461064}, {"id": 47890, "content": "只看小撒和老胡。只记得老胡", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 378446}, {"id": 50962, "content": "没六小龄童，还有那个卖骚的春晚总导演说给春晚打一百分。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476772}]}